span.font: DAG representation of the 21 task, "join" workflow, used in this activity. The initial 20 tasks, labeled "task0" to "task19", are computationally expensive and require 3600 TFlops to compute. The final task, "task20", which depends on all other tasks, requires only 300 TFlops to compute. All files used in this workflow consume 2000 MB of disk space.
